{"tid":15657,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 手機電力 vs 厚度","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T10:22:03.000Z","uid":30830,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b9b59d959ac07aa10acfb36365f2ed8cf69f35","tid":15657,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"智能手機慢慢發展，電力同 CPU 用力量都齊齊加大<br />\n而家大部份嘅機加去到3000mAh 就開始停 (唔計大芒機) <br />\n為咗要薄，仲要有啲廠減細粒電轉頭得番二千六，二千八<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔明，又要薄，又要唔夠電，個相機鏡頭又突出嚟，我就寧願部機加多5mm, 粒電加多四五百 mAh, 起碼部機夠我狂打機打成日都唔怕無電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲點睇，要薄定要電 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(唔好同我講話新技術又要薄又要多電，而家成日新聞都話有新技術，但係從來未見到有量產化) <br />\n<br />\n唔怕厚，要多啲電！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怕無電，要更輕！要更薄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdbe58450e009aded515cf837f33fc585f50437","tid":15657,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"用緊小米mix 4400mah <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415f5c1df4ceba1cbffdaeab613c8683ccaffa22","tid":15657,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊小米mix 4400mah <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好意思講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537dc09b5a4a5cb9a1885a0f6ad9f0da795d5e3e","tid":15657,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"其實iphone 都已經太薄，冇殼拎上手係好唔自然"},{"pid":"d327a3513b6ce9e5f40626e5059403227c5fd2fe","tid":15657,"uid":45276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"薄 加可換電先會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1935a1d22a14c825a8225a607a3cf9998